=======
# Use your IP address as the hostname for development and testing of Keycloak.
# NOTE: Named APP_HOSTNAME (not HOSTNAME) because bash exports HOSTNAME as a
# built-in short machine name, which would override a value set here when
# compose interpolates ${APP_HOSTNAME} at up-time.
APP_HOSTNAME=aems.local
# Optional: set to your machine's LAN IP to include it as a SAN in the local cert.
# The volume 'certs-data' will need to be deleted and certs container restarted
# after changing this value.
HOST_IP=

